Directed by Aditya Datt

Written by Junaid Wasi. Vipul Amrutlal Shah. Junaid Wasi

Puneet Dehran (Foot Solider 4 (as Puneet Dehraan)). Manoj Singh Kaira (Foot Soldier 5). Krish Dhangar (Foot Soldier 6). Abhishek Dubey (Foot Soldier 7). Suraj Naagar (Foot Soldier 8). Dharmendra Gupta (Nayaran). Vibhawari Deshpande (Rajani). Veerendra Saxena (Ahmed (as Virendra Saxena)). Rajesh Tailang(Roy). Udit Ohri (Indian Officer). Shireesh Sharma (ATS Chief). Gracy Goswami (School Girl 1 (as Gracy Bitin Goswami)). Rose Khan (School Girl 2). Navdeep Tomar (Pehelwaan). Vidyut Jammwal (Karan (as Vidyut Jammwal) (as Vidyut Jaamwal: end credits)). Pradeep Rawal (Police Constable). Atharva Vishwakarma (Abeer). Puneet Channa (Sahil). Angira Dhar (Malika). Andy von Eich (BI Officer (as Andy Von Eich)). Mark Bennington (Alvin). Sajeb Ali (Buraq’s Assistant). Alexander Schlaefke (Zaytune). Yakshitt Rroy (Foot Soldier 10 (as Suresh Kumar)). Anil Khopkar (Maulvi). Jeet Matharu (Momin’s Man). Pooja Singh (Indian Journalist Female). Aashin A. Shah (Indian Journalist (as Aasin Shah)). Richard Bhakti Klein (BI Officer (as R. Bhakti Klein)). Jairoop Jeevan (Defence Minister). Kalpesh (Indian Constable). Tanya Purohit (Indian News Anchor). Ashish Sharma (Ram). Atul Bandi (Ram (as Dr Atul Bandi)). Om Kumar (Lakshman). Pratiksha Nayyar (Sita). Ajay Saroz Yadav (Ravan). Prabhanshu Choubey (Hanuman). Jeetraj Singh (Meghnath). Aniket Mishra (Vibhishan). Hemlata Kesri (Rani). Pulkit Dixit (Angad). Vijay Owhal (Jamwant). Govardhanlal Sourashtriya (Rakshas). Rahul Singh Tomar (Additional Foot Soldier). Sanki Shailendra (Additional Foot Soldier). Zaid Ahmad Khan (Additional Foot Soldier). Sahil Suda (Additional Foot Soldier) . Nileshpatelxyz (Shaurya). Manoj Anand (Suspect Pathan (uncredited)). Ian Austin (MI5 Agent / Soldier (uncredited)). Sibaa Awan (Hotel Patron (uncredited)). Michael Barlow (Peter Armed Response Officer (uncredited)). Brett Bull (School Student (uncredited)). Waqas Danish (Suspect (uncredited)). Sahil Rakesh Grover (Welder (uncredited)). Juke Hardy ((uncredited)). Zarine Hussain (Asian Pedestrian (uncredited)). Joanne James (Passerby (uncredited)). Vicky Kadian (Vicky (uncredited)). Jess Kaur (Pedestrian (uncredited)). Simran Kaur (Pedestrian (uncredited)). Sujit Kumar Mishra (Munna (uncredited)). Goran Mitrovski (Military Guard (uncredited)). Navdeep Monga (Murder Suspect (uncredited)). Kwok Ng(Secret Agent Spy (uncredited)). Nirjar Patel (Terrorist (uncredited)). Taavi Peelo (Suspect (uncredited)). Sarah Pitts (Pedestrian (uncredited)). Felix Fukuyoshi Ruwwe (Mercenary #2 (uncredited)). Lorenz Hideyoshi Ruwwe (Mercenary #1 (uncredited)). Stephen Seal (Henchman (uncredited)). Mandeep Sehmi (Hotel Patron (uncredited)). Shahzad Shah (Suspect (uncredited)). Sonal Simon (Suspect (uncredited)). Mandeep Singh (Abeer Khan Small Baby (uncredited))

Languages Hindi

Producers Bhavin Bhanushali. Sam Bhattacharjee. Tanya Chadha. Amit Chandrra. Pradeep Jaiswal. Firuzi Khan. Ravichand Nallappa. Deepshikha Nandini. Sachin Savla. Aashin A. Shah. Vipul Amrutlal Shah. Chetan Sharma. Jigyasa Sharma. Adi Sharmaa. Laure Vaysse

Production Reliance Entertainment. Motion Picture Capita. Sunshine Picture
